E_D("replace into `wp_posts` values('799','1','2012-07-28 12:07:15','2012-07-28 04:07:15','今年没有去chinajoy，本来想去抢东西的，比如抱枕，雨伞，箱子诸如此类。\r\n\r\n不过我终于知道怎么形容最近的心情了，就是你在地铁里，听着音乐，居然莫名发觉口袋里空荡荡的，用手一抄，钱包不见了，瞬时心头一震，菊花一紧，百感交集，无力虚弱之感油然而起，无数复杂的情感涌上心头，再一摸，所幸还在，却始终感觉空落落的。\r\n\r\n所以我还是太年轻了，在过去的岁月里，总是以为万物运行皆有其理，因而无法摆脱强迫症的束缚，总想分析出事物所有的可能性，选择其概率最大风险最低的那个。然而悲剧在于大多数情况下可能性太多，优先级和概念根本无法判断。在最初的最初，整个循环就已经溢出了。\r\n\r\n旅行的意义，\r\n或是终于离开家了，真好；\r\n或是终于回到家了，真好。\r\n所以我们相聚相别，\r\n或是为了还能再见，真好，\r\n或为了相见恨晚，真好。\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">去年今日此门中，</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">人面桃花相映红。</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">人面不知何处去，</h1>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">桃花依旧笑春风。</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.xiezezhun.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/2012-7-27.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-800 aligncenter\" title=\"2012-7-27\" src=\"http://www.xiezezhun.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/2012-7-27.jpg\" alt=\"www.xiezezhun.com\" width=\"384\" height=\"288\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n固定链接：<a href=\"http://www.xiezezhun.com/799.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.xiezezhun.com/799.html</a>','2012 chinajoy','','publish','open','open','','2012-chinajoy','','','2013-04-15 13:11:05','2013-04-15 05:11:05','','0','http://xiezezhun.com/?p=799','0','post','','2');");
E_D("replace into `wp_posts` values('791','1','2012-07-11 23:32:47','2012-07-11 15:32:47','1、一开始A和B都吃一颗苹果，下班前A和B都吃完了，吃了一阵子后……\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n2、主管要B再吃一颗苹果，结果A和B在下班前也都吃完了。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td colspan=\"0\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n3、主管觉得应该要公平，所以也给A多一个苹果，结果A和B在下班前也都吃完了。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n4、主管觉得可以再给B一个苹果\r\nA下班前都吃完了。\r\nB下班后留下来一阵子才吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">  </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n5、主管觉得B很认真负责留下来把苹果吃完，为什么A总是可以准时下班，于是也给A一个苹果。\r\nA还是下班前都吃完了。\r\nB还是下班后留下来一阵子才吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n6、主管觉得A工作能力很强，可以被信任，于是再给A一个苹果\r\nA下班后留下来一阵子后才吃完。\r\nB也是下班后留下来一阵子才吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">  </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n7、主管觉得A和B都很认真，很有责任感，肯花时间把东西做完才回家\r\n于是A每天都吃四个苹果，\r\nB每天都吃3个苹果，又吃了一阵子后……\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">  </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n8、某一天，公司有了新政策，多了一项例行性的业务（苹果），主管想说A已经吃了4哥苹果，所以吧苹果给了B，二人刚好都是4颗。\r\nA还是下班后留下一阵子才吃完，\r\nB开始下班后要留下来很久才能吃得完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n9、主管注意到A和B都要流下来才能吃得完，但又不想花钱请人，\r\n所A和B每天都吃4个苹果，都是下班后留下来才吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> A </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n10、终于A不爽了，每天都要留下来硬吃才能吃得完，于是离职了。\r\n来一个C，因为C刚来业务不熟，一天只能先吃2个，另外2个给B，所以B一天要吃6个。\r\nC下班就吃完了。\r\nB下班后要留到半夜才能吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n11、主管觉得可以让C再吃一个，所以吧B的一个苹果丢给C，\r\nC下班就吃完了，\r\nB还是下班后要留到半夜才能吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n12、业务回到两个人每天都吃四个苹果。\r\nC开始下班后要留下来才吃完。\r\nB还是下班后要留下来才能吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n13、B开始抱怨每天都要留下来才吃的完（B从4开始就每天留下来），\r\nC才觉得奇怪，才来几天就要留下来才吃的完。\r\nB和C每天都要留下来才吃的完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> B </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n14、B终于受不了了，他辞职了，来了一个D接B的位子。主管觉得B以前每天都吃4个苹果，所以用同样的标准，也给D吃4个苹果，因为C刚来无法把苹果丢给D。\r\nC和D每天都要留下来才吃的完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n15、C和D觉得好辛苦，才刚来就要加班留下来。员工很辛苦吃苹果，公司赚钱了，又多了客户，过一个苹果可以吃，主管把苹果丢给C，因为他来的比较久。\r\nC和D每天都要留下来才吃的完。\r\nC留的更晚了。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> C </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n16、C也不爽了，才刚来就要吃这么多苹果，于是离职。\r\n主观意识到苹果可能太多吃不完，于是多请一个人来吃。来了E和F，同时工作重新分配，每人每天吃三个苹果。\r\nD终于可以下班吃完。\r\nEF才刚来就要吃3个苹果，但勉强可以吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n17、主管觉得多了一个人，应该可以多接些业务，于是多一个苹果给D，\r\nD又开始需要留下来吃完苹果。\r\nEF同样下班就吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n18、D觉得很累，自己刚来还不太熟就要吃4个苹果，E和F什么都不懂，问D也问不出所以然，三个都很迷惑。\r\nD还是留下来吃完苹果。\r\nEF同样下班就吃完。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n19、主管发现E和F每天都准时下班，可能太闲，于是分别给两人多一个苹果。\r\n三个人开始留下来才能吃完苹果。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n20、就这样EDF三个人每天都吃四个苹果，主管觉得公司很稳定成长。\r\n三个人还是每天都留下来才能吃完苹果。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n21、公司一直成长，当然会有新的想法新的作为，某天，又多了新政策，主管把新政策丢给E，可能他比较适合吃这个苹果。\r\n三个人还是每天都留下来才能吃完苹果。\r\n但E留更晚了。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> D </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> E </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> F </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; f