r\n马上就找到G，H，I三个人，三个人都是新人，没得挑，只能接前一个人的苹果。\r\nGHI觉得好夸张，都是新人就要吃这么多，其中H的抗压性低，马上就离开了。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> G </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> H </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> I </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\">   </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n24、主管只能再找一个人来，于是来了一个J。\r\nG天生很会吃苹果，虽然刚来但下班就吃完了，留下J和I下班后吃苹果。\r\n<table style=\"border: 1px solid #000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> G </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: xx-large;\"> ● </span></td>\r\n<td><s